data.description: Charming 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom townhome situated in a highly sought after neighborhood, offering the perfect blend of convenience and style! As you enter, you'll be greeted by a bright and inviting entryway. The first bedroom is strategically located off entry with a nearby full bathroom featuring a stand-up shower. Kitchen boasts granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and an eat-in area for casual dining. The laundry room features convenient cabinet storage and a pull-down attic entry, providing ample space for all your storage needs. A versatile room with gorgeous French doors awaits, offering the perfect opportunity for a third bedroom, home office, or flex space tailored to your lifestyle. The spacious living area, adorned with a vaulted ceiling, creates an open and airy atmosphere, perfect for entertaining friends and family. The primary suite is a sanctuary of comfort and style, featuring abundant natural light, an en suite bathroom with a double sink vanity, a shower-tub combo, and a large walk-in closet. Relax and unwind in your private oasis after a long day. Step outside to your fenced back patio space, complete with a storage closet, providing a serene outdoor retreat for enjoying morning coffee or evening gatherings. The convenience of a one-car garage adds to the property's appeal, offering secure parking and additional storage options. This townhome is not just a residence; it's a lifestyle. Enjoy the ease of living in a well-sought neighborhood, just minutes from the vibrant heart of downtown Aiken!
